cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the application of machine learning algorithms for filtering unwanted electronic mail messages, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The use of boosting algorithms and decision trees also suggests the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
